CGA folder includes example program showing usage of Compal GPU Annealer.

Example 1.
  tsp-demo.py using CGA 1.0 API 
Example 2.
  maxcut_sample.py using CGA 2.0 API support init_spin variable 

CGA 2.0 package at ./CGA2.0-release folder
Steps to install 
Step 1. Download and unzip CGA2.0 package file compal_solver_nstc-2.0.0-py3-none-any.whl
    7z x cga2.0-release.7z -p"password"
Step 2. uninstall old compal_solver 
    pip uninstall compal_solver-nstc
Step 3. install CGA2.0
    pip install ./compal_solver_nstc-2.0.0-py3-none-any.whl
